snippet.textDisplay: This song has the potential to be one of the all time greats of Coke studio. A very powerful song from the music arrangement, lyrics, message of the song to the eventual vocals and definitely the highlight of this season so far. On a personal level, this has to be the best performance of Jaswal to date. Ahmed Jahanzeb was a very smart pick and he did his part as expected brilliantly bringing the softness and a different dimension in comparison to Jaswal's powerful but crude voice. The two of them singing in unison was a treat to watch and listen. All thumbs and toes up for Shuja Haider; 10/10 for both 'Aaqa' and 'Khaki banda'.
